name: I Flew Porter's INAUGURAL Embraer E2 Flight!
description:
On February 1st, Porter launched commercial flights with their brand-new Embraer E195-E2s, and their very first flight was a short hop from Toronto-Pearson to Ottawa!

As the North American launch customer, this was also the very first commercial E2 flight in North America. This is also a pretty big deal for Porter, as it marks the start of a very rapid expansion.

Let's see what Porter has to offer on these new planes!
